{"id":"59313baa-ce9e-4f44-b570-2dc163511828","name":"Entry #1 \"白日夢...\"","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">I used to have many dreams.</h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Some good.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Some forgettable.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Some bad enough to wake me up breathing too fast.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">But at least they were normal.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">At least <strong>they</strong> were mine.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Now... I sleep almost not at all.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">And when I do, I don’t fall into night.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">I fall into daylight—a perfect imitation of my own home, every corner identical, every object exactly where I left it.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">Except for one thing.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">I’m alone.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">I was alone.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">--</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">No parents.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No neighbors.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No passing cars.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No birds.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">No sky outside the window—only a pale, empty white, as if whoever built this place forgot that the world needs a horizon.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">I never know how I get here.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">I never remember lying down.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The dream just... opens its eyes before I do.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">And in the living room, the television is always on.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Static.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Black, white, gray—never color.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Just a storm of noise frozen in a rectangle.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">At first I thought it was a glitch.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Then I thought it was a nightmare.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Then I realized I wasn’t waking up.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">And then I saw <strong><u>it</u></strong>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Slowly rising up on the screen of TV .</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">His pale look, of judgment never even blink.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">It speaks, but not with one voice.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Sometimes it sounds like news anchors.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Sometimes like children’s shows.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Sometimes like emergency broadcasts.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Sometimes like something that isn’t a voice at all, but cold air vibrating.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"mxkWcQg7zW0Ltl0xef_ju.webp","creator":"Bot-ZI4","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🔦 Horror"],"chats":42,"messages":366,"created_at":"2025-11-29T11:05:00.812518+00:00"}